<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div>
<p>Been working on this a little while. It's a bit longer than my tales normally are, but I resisted the urge to shorten it considerably. Lemme know what you think.</p>
<p>Edit: Also should thank Zolgamax, Decibelle, TwistedGears, Von Pincier, and others for helping me with refining this. It was a little rough when I created my first draft, but it's a lot smoother now.</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div id="u-author_block">
